Save time and money on the road
Refuel and wash your car with one app. With every refuel, you get a discount of at least 2 cents/liter from gasoline and diesel. Download the free St1 Way app and take advantage of fuel discounts and other benefits today!

Key Features:
•	Pay for refueling with your phone at over 400 St1 and Shell gas stations across Finland.
•	Save at least 2 cents per liter on every refuel.
•	Buy Perfect car washes at the best price directly from the app.
•	Benefit from exclusive mobile offers and head to HelmiSimpukka.
•	Find the nearest St1 or Shell station with the station finder.
•	Pay with your credit or debit card (Visa or Mastercard) or ApplePay.
•	Receive a digital receipt from your refuel directly to your phone. Forget paper receipts and help the environment.

Refuel with the app
Welcome to the modern service station! Pay for car’s gasoline or diesel smoothly and securely with the St1 Way app. Log in, add your preferred payment method, drive up to a free pump, choose the pump number, payment method (Visa, Mastercard, or ApplePay) and maximum euro amount in the app. Start fueling as usual. Once you've finished fueling, the receipt will be conveniently available in the St1 Way app, so you can skip the hassle of dealing with paper copies altogether. Mobile fueling is available at over 400 St1 and Shell stations across Finland.

Save money on every refuel
Whenever you refuel your gasoline or diesel car using your phone, you’ll enjoy a discount of at least 2 cents per liter. Mobile fueling makes your traveling easier and cheaper.

Buy and manage Perfect car washes
Purchase Perfect car washes directly from the app and keep your car clean in all situations. Select the ideal car wash for every season and keep your car clean without any effort! Perfect car wash uses gentle, specialized brushes to give your car a safe and thorough clean. All wash codes purchased from the app can be used at nearly 70 Perfect wash stations and are valid for 5 months from the purchase date.

Exclusive benefits for St1 Way app users
As a St1 Way app user, you can enjoy unique benefits available only through the app. In the benefits section, you'll also find weekly changing offers from HelmiSimpukka.

Check HelmiSimpukka menus before visiting
HelmiSimpukka Restaurants and HelmiSimpukka Express stations are located at St1 and Shell stations. In the St1 Way app, you can browse menus, including 24-hour options, Helmi classics, pizzas, hot dogs, burgers – without forgetting the kids' favorites. 
HelmiSimpukka’s menu highlights handcrafted items. And let’s not forget fresh coffee adding the perfect touch to any day.
Plan your meals and breaks as part of your journey. Remember to take advantage of mobile benefits and special offers at HelmiSimpukka restaurants. Follow weekly offers and save money on the go by using the best deals on food and drinks.

Find the nearest station and optimize your route
Optimize your route with the map feature – find the nearest service station, fueling point, electric charging, car wash, or HelmiSimpukka restaurant and navigate there with ease. Your device's built-in Maps app manages navigation, guiding you to your destination.
Filtering locations is also a very handy feature in the St1 Way app. Filter your search to find the services you need, such as specific fuel types or the nearest electric charging point.

Forget paper fuel receipts – help the environment
Keep your fueling receipts in the St1 Way app and reduce paper usage. You can find all your receipts from the Receipts folder in the Profile section, where you can easily share them, for instance, with your company’s bookkeeping.

Download St1 Way now and make your journey smoother!

PROPS TO YOU

What if every decision you make—big or small—could bring you something valuable? Welcome to Props, where everyday choices turn into real money.
Props are a virtual currency you earn in many different ways every day. You can use Props to pay at dozens of well-known stores and chains as well as online.

How to earn Props

From purchases: activate an offer, buy, and snap a photo of the receipt—or collect automatically by linking your payment card.
From tasks & challenges: complete daily and weekly tasks, collect bonus rounds.
From surveys: answer quick opinion and NPS surveys in connection with your purchase.
From trials & sign-ups: try services or start free trials from our partners.
From steps & wellbeing: earn every day from your steps (once you’ve connected your health data).
From friend invites: share an invite—when your friend joins and becomes active, you both earn.
From online shopping: shop at partner stores via Props links.

Claim the Props you’ve earned right away and start earning more today!

How Props works:

1. Live Your Life, Earn Props: Make everyday choices—what you buy, what you eat, where you shop. Earn Props effortlessly for every action.
2. Track & collect: Use the Props app and watch your balance grow with every decision. Your lifestyle becomes your most valuable asset.
3. Spend or Save: Redeem your Props for discounts, gift cards, and exclusive offers—or save them for a bigger goal. You decide!

Why You’ll Love Props

It’s easy and fun to rack up Props every day. In Props you’ll find contests, tasks, perks, offers, and surprises that help you earn even more. The more you use Props in your daily life, the more you earn.

- Effortless Earning: Every decision counts, with no extra hassle
- Real Rewards: Shop, save, or treat yourself—Props are money
- Made for You: Earn more from the brands and actions you already love

Every Choice Matters

Whether it’s grabbing a coffee, choosing eco-friendly products, or trying something new, your decisions shape your day—and now your wallet, too.
Ready to Get Started?


Download Props today and see how easy it is to earn with your everyday decisions. Your next great choice is just a tap away!

HINGE, DESIGNED TO BE DELETED
Hinge is the dating app for people who want to get off of dating apps. With profiles that show your personality through text, photos, video, and voice, you have unique conversations that lead to great dates. And it’s working. Currently, people on Hinge go on a date every three seconds. Additionally, in 2022, we were the fastest-growing dating app in the US, UK, and Canada.

HOW WE GET YOU OFF HINGE
When it comes to online dating, people are so busy matching that they’re not actually connecting, in person, where it counts. Hinge is on a mission to change that. So we built an app that’s designed to be deleted. Here’s how:

* We quickly learn your type. You’ll only be introduced to the best people for you.

* We give you a sense of someone’s personality. You’ll get to know potential dates through their unique answers to prompts, as well as information like religion, height, politics, dating intentions, relationship type, and much more.

* We make it easy to start a conversation. Every match begins by someone liking or commenting on a specific part of your profile.

* We want you to feel confident about meeting people in person. Selfie Verification makes it easier for daters on Hinge to ensure that they are who they say they are.

* We ask how your dates are going. After exchanging phone numbers with a Match, we’ll follow up to hear how your date went so we can make better recommendations in the future.

The app is free to use. Members looking to see everyone who likes them or send unlimited likes can upgrade to Hinge+. To access additional features, including enhanced recommendations and priority likes, we offer HingeX.

PRESS
"It's the go-to dating app for many people looking for love." - The Daily Mail
“Hinge’s CEO says a good dating app relies on vulnerability, not algorithms.” - Washington Post
"Hinge is the first dating app to actually measure real-world success" - TechCrunch

Roborock App is a dedicated application designed to control Roborock’s smart hardware devices. 
It supports network-enabled products in Roborock’s robotic vacuum cleaners, wet and dry vacuum cleaners, and molecular sieve-based washer dryers.
You can remotely control smart devices and check their status and cleaning progress through this app anytime, anywhere.
Easily unlock more advanced features through the Roborock app.

【Roborock Robotic Vacuum Cleaner】
· Check the cleaning map and path anywhere and anytime you want, and control the cleaning progress in real-time. 
· Choose from various personalized cleaning methods, including room cleaning, zone cleaning, scheduled cleaning, and spot cleaning routines.
· Set up frequently used cleaning tasks as routines for one-tap starts. 
· Choose multiple cleaning preferences, including Vacuum, Mop, Vac & Mop, SmartPlan (applicable to certain models only), and Customize mode. 
· Set up a personalized cleaning plan by adjusting suction power, water flow, cleaning frequency, and route (applicable to certain models only).
· Enables you to edit a map based on your home and set names for thresholds, carpets, floor types, furniture, and rooms. 
· Set up invisible walls and no-go zones and your robot will not cross or enter them during cleaning.
· Enjoy a variety of fun features, including remote viewing, obstacle photos, pet snapshots, cruise mode, pet search, and custom tones (applicable to select models only).

【Roborock Wet and Dry Vacuum Cleaner】
· Adjust water flow, suction power, roller speed, and detergent level (applicable to select models only) based on the floor and dirt level.
· Smart scheduled self-cleaning and drying: automatically initiates self-cleaning and drying based on historical operation records.

【Roborock Washer Dryer】
· Check the washing progress and operating status anywhere and anytime you want.
· Choose from over 20 smart washing and drying programs to meet the professional needs of various fabrics and clothing, ensuring optimal washing performance.
· Set one program as the App Program for quick access on the control panel.

【Permissions】
To provide certain services, you need to enable the relevant permissions on your mobile device. We will only need the relevant permissions and access your personal information (if relevant) when you use the relevant functions. For the optional permissions, you can refuse or withdraw these permissions at any time, for which you may not be able to use the corresponding services, but this will not affect other functions of the App. The current permissions that the app may need are as follows: 
· Location (Optional)
Accesses location information to connect to WiFi, find nearby devices ready for connection, and retrieve details about the current WiFi connection.
· Camera (Optional)
Enables the camera to scan QR codes for easier WiFi connection.
· Photos (Optional)
Allows access to photos for uploading profile pictures and attaching images when providing feedback. If your device supports features like downloading obstacle images, taking screenshots, or recording during remote viewing, photos and videos can be stored.
· Microphone (Optional)
Used for sound transmission on devices that support remote viewing.
· WLAN (Optional)
Facilitates connection to WiFi networks emitted by smart devices for communication and connectivity.
· Bluetooth (Optional)
Enables connection to Bluetooth signals from smart devices for communication and device connecting.
· Notifications (Optional)
Allows the app to send you device and system notifications.
· Local Network (Optional)
When connecting devices on the iOS local network, grants access to the local network to connect to WiFi networks emitted by smart devices.
· Siri & Search (Optional)
When opening Siri on iOS, interacts with Siri to control the starting and moving of devices based on the Routines set up in the mobile device.

Oikotie – Myytävät ja vuokra-asunnot

Oikotie-sovelluksella löydät nopeasti uudet myytävät ja vuokrattavat asunnot. Selaa vaihtoehtoja missä ja milloin tahansa, rajaa hakua omien toiveidesi mukaan ja tallenna suosikit sydämellä. Kun luot hakuvahdin, saat ilmoituksia suoraan puhelimeesi – unelmiesi koti voi olla vain yhden klikkauksen päässä.

Ilmoitukset uusista kohteista
Kun teet hakuvahdin, saat ilmoituksen heti, kun hakukriteerejäsi vastaava asunto julkaistaan. Pysy ajan tasalla ja toimi nopeasti – muista sallia push-ilmoitukset, jotta et jää mistään paitsi.

Helppo asuntohaku ja karttarajaus
Valitse sinulle tärkeät kriteerit, kuten sijainti, hinta, pinta-ala ja talotyyppi. Voit myös rajata haun suoraan kartalle piirtämällä – löydät helposti juuri ne alueet, jotka sinua kiinnostavat.

Tallenna suosikit ja tärkeät haut
Merkitse kiinnostavat kodit sydämellä ja ota käyttöön hakuvahti. Sen avulla pysyt ajan tasalla uusista mahdollisuuksista ilman jatkuvaa selaamista.

Löydät helposti takaisin
Suosikit ja hakuvahtisi säilyvät tallessa – löydät ne helposti Suosikit- ja Vahdit-näkymistä, kun haluat palata kiinnostaviin kohteisiin.

Kehitämme jatkuvasti
Oikotie-sovellusta kehitetään yhdessä käyttäjien kanssa. Voit antaa palautetta suoraan sovelluksessa tai osoitteessa oikotie.fi/palaute.

Lataa Oikotie ja aloita kotisi etsintä jo tänään.

Löydä juuri sinulle sopiva asunto

Etuovi.com, siellä ne kaikki asunnot on. Nyt löydät kaikki myytävät asunnot myös Etuovi.com-sovelluksesta. Lataa heti, saat nopeimmin tiedon uusista kiinnostavista asunnoista. 

Asunnon hakeminen entistä sujuvammaksi

Hae sujuvasti kartalta, käytä omaa sijaintiasi rajauksena tai rajaa hakua kattavimpien hakuehtojen avulla – vaikka lämmitysmuodon mukaan. Suosituimman asuntohaun odotettu sovellus tarjoaa koko Suomen myytävät asunnot välittäjiltä, rakennuttajilta ja yksityisiltä myyjiltä. 
Ensimmäisenä palveluna Suomessa Etuovi.com tarjoaa sinulle uuden tavan hakea myytäviä asuntoja ja loma-asuntoja: voit määrittää hakukriteeriksi matka-ajan sinulle tärkeästä sijainnista, oli se sitten työpaikka, lasten koulu tai vaikkapa mummola. Matka-aikahaku on saatavilla vain Etuovi.comin sovelluksessa!
Suomen informatiivisin kartta myynti-ilmoituksessa

Klikkaa myynti-ilmoituksen Kohde kartalla -linkkiä. Loistavan tarkka kartta kertoo asunnon sijainnin, tontin rajat, alueen muut rakennukset sekä liikenneyhteydet ja lähipalvelut.

Tallenna suosikiksi tai hakuvahdiksi

Klikkaa sydäntä tai swaippaa kohde hakutuloslistalta oikealle, niin asunto tallentuu suosikkilistallesi. Luo hakuvahti -linkin klikkauksella tallennat helposti tärkeimmät hakusi. Vahdit ja suosikit löytyvät Tallennetut-näkymästä, missä voit helposti muokata niitä.

I Am Sober is more than just a free sobriety counter app.

Along with tracking your sober days, it helps you build new habits and provides ongoing motivation by connecting you to a wide network of people all striving for the same goal: staying sober one day at a time.

Through our growing sober community you can learn from others and contribute by sharing insights and tactics that have worked for you.

**The I Am Sober app features:**

• Sober day tracker
To visualize how long you’ve been sober.

• Remember why you quit
Add reasons and photos to help you remember why you want to quit your addiction and stay sober.

• Daily pledge tracker
Take a pledge every day. Sobriety is a 24-hour struggle, so start your day off by making a pledge to stay sober. Then you can review how your day went and log notes at the end of the day.

• Sobriety calculator
View how much money & time you’ve saved by being sober.

• Analyze triggers
Recap each day and find patterns that made your day easier or more challenging than the last.

• Share your story
Either with others or for yourself, take photos and journal your progress directly in the app. Then choose to share it or save it as a reminder for yourself.

• Milestone tracker
Track and celebrate your milestones from 1 day, to 1 week, to 1 month and beyond. Compare experiences with others on their sober journey. Read how they felt at this milestone and what you can expect. If you’re struggling, share your story and invite others to offer help or advice.

• Withdrawal timeline
When you create an account and declare your addiction, you can instantly see a withdrawal timeline to get an idea of what to expect for your next few days (and weeks). What’s more, you can contribute to it. See how many others saw an increase in their restfulness vs those that saw an increase in anxiety. Prepare yourself for what’s to come in recovery.

• Customize your experience
You set the time, your sober birthday, the category of motivation you need, the addictions you’re trying to break, even the end-of-day summaries. Make the app customized to your lifestyle and tailored to your needs.

**Sober Plus subscriptions**

I Am Sober is free to use, but you can support development of the app with a subscription to Sober Plus. With Sober Plus, you'll get access to these premium features:

• Create a group
Stay accountable together and track your sobriety privately. Groups are great for complimenting your real-world group like Alcoholics Anonymous, NA, SA, SMART Recovery, or your rehab center.

• Locked access
Keep your trackers private with a lock that you can access via TouchID or FaceID.

• Data Backups
Save your progress in the cloud and restore your trackers if you get a new device.

• More tracking
Track more addictions and get access to more communities. Even if your addiction is specific like Wine, Online Shopping, or Skin Picking, you’ll find a variety of communities of people who are all trying to get sober from alcohol, drugs, eating disorders, self-harm, and more.
